  <p>Playing <strong>Ludo King</strong> online is simple and fun for everyone!</p>
  
  <p><strong>Mouse or Touch:</strong> Click or tap on the dice to roll. Then, select your token and tap again to move it according to the dice number.</p>
  
  <p><strong>Keyboard Shortcuts:</strong> Use the arrow keys (← ↑ ↓ →) to highlight tokens, and press <strong>Enter</strong> to move the selected token. Press the <strong>Space bar</strong> to roll the dice quickly.</p>
  
  <p><strong>Quick Restart:</strong> Want to begin a new match? Press <strong>R</strong> to reset the board and start fresh.</p>
  
  <p>No downloads or installations needed—just open your browser and enjoy the classic family board game. Perfect for practicing strategy, patience, and having fun with friends!</p>
